{"tid":1021190,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"Fresh Grad搵工薪金唔可以太低","createTime":"2019-02-14T05:54:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T09:09:17.000Z","uid":196627,"like":40,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"ea6fdce152579759615eb449ee323435a3f5f931","tid":1021190,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:54:42.000Z","msg":"就快就到新既一批畢業生出來返工<br />\n不過我去年發現<br />\n有好多大學生以為自己咩經驗都無<br />\n就對自己工作能力冇信心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個Expected Salary居然寫萬一,二<br />\n食個飯都四五十<br />\n坐車一日都二三十<br />\n已經唔講買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wfc.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有俾家用，還學債，供保險，投資，草錢，電話費，情人節行街睇戲食飯？<br />\n一萬頭月薪既生活<br />\n做狗都好過做人喇！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我見過有幾個無經驗既candidates<br />\n佢地比我既感覺唔錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我打算比個機會佢地<br />\n但係佢地個Expected Salary就真係低得太離譜啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你自己都唔尊重自己<br />\n邊個會尊重你呀<br />\n公司都唔會對你有信心喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咁我咪用個較為恰當既工資($18000~$20000)比個offer佢地囉<br />\n<br />\n但係佢地一聽個Offer之後<br />\n個個都o撚曬嘴<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話自己Handle唔到工作內容<br />\n然後就放棄左呢個機會<br />\n<br />\n講真<br />\n大學生一畢業咩經驗都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/silly.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n雖然公司請你仲要教埋你<br />\n根本就我地公司蝕低<br />\n但細心諗諗<br />\n包括我在內有邊個Fresh Grad唔係白紙一張呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都肯比機會你<br />\n仲比埋人工你<br />\n點解都要咁冇信心呢?<br />\n就咁樣佢地就失去呢個寶貴既機會啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以<br />\n各位將要畢業既同學<br />\n唔好再俾hr壓價喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n對自己有信心<br />\n你四年大學學到既野<br />\n已經係你地最大既本錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ccae834c0c15c1703ed3886223ac82162af0319","tid":1021190,"uid":196627,"like":6,"dislike":8,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:54:54.000Z","msg":"我個post完全唔係for笑<br />\n公司目的係利潤最大化<br />\n目的係警惕所有應徵者<br />\n幫大部分幼稚連登仔建立正確工作價值觀<br />\n要笑既可以正評後出翻去"},{"pid":"380ea5e0b4f8d0f97fdc81838af29fdcfed32df7","tid":1021190,"uid":128894,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:56:40.000Z","msg":"做乜撚野<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c8b91e1424fd6bf35fcd838c2eb85ab342cfcfd","tid":1021190,"uid":9457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"轉死性<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a827198399397a218367feaa2087d4756c986fcb","tid":1021190,"uid":40470,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:58:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n跟住樓主自己搵工開12k<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nBtw<br />\n<br />\n你地諗下aco 13k點解咁多大學生爭？"},{"pid":"cb9d898cbfd09c37c56dd1dada44ba97af2e8221","tid":1021190,"uid":77731,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:00:18.000Z","msg":"你只係一條呃人佣金既headhunt狗<br />\n你要人寫高expected salary純粹出於你可以刮多d佣"},{"pid":"13d1d99d035f2429f326f28856516d38045d375e","tid":1021190,"uid":26429,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T06:00:54.000Z","msg":"Hr<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6550838b7acfb69b8265e8e763b0c2e15a065fe3","tid":1021190,"uid":196627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7c8b91e1424fd6bf35fcd838c2eb85ab342cfcfd","tid":1021190,"uid":9457,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T05:56:49.000Z","msg":"轉死性<img src=\"/asset